PN,30401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThere was "no requirement" for Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer to formally interview
OL,9,FLord Mandelson for the US
OL,10,Fambassadorship, Downing Street has
OL,11,Fsaid amid accusations of a lack of
OL,12,Fprime ministerial involvement in the
OL,13,Fappointment.
OL,15,FNo 10 conceded there were "lessons to
OL,16,Fbe learned" from the process but
OL,17,Finsisted due diligence was followed
OL,18,Fbefore the peer was given the
OL,19,FWashington job.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@ZO]wD@[OUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Tories have questioned the absence
OL,8,Fof input from Starmer in published
OL,9,Fdocuments relating to the appointment,
OL,10,Fand asked his independent ethics
OL,11,Fadviser Sir Laurie Magnus to
OL,12,Finvestigate whether the ministerial
OL,13,Fcode has been breached.
OL,15,FSir Laurie, the independent adviser on
OL,16,Fministerial standards, said there were
OL,17,Fno grounds for an investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"I consider that the documentation
OL,8,Fthat has been made public indicates
OL,9,Fthat the relevant process for a
OL,10,Fpolitical appointee was followed," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAsked on Friday whether the prime
OL,8,Fminister had spoken to Lord Mandelson
OL,9,Fbefore giving him the UK's most
OL,10,Fprestigious diplomatic posting abroad,
OL,11,FDowning Street said the "full process
OL,12,Fat the time of the appointment was
OL,13,Ffollowed".
OL,15,FStarmer's official spokesman said:
OL,16,F"There was no requirement for a formal
OL,17,Finterview with the prime minister."
OL,26,@sD@YOUuD@IO]xD@AOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FDetails of Lord Mandelson's
OL,8,Fappointment and subsequent removal
OL,9,Ffrom the Washington job have been
OL,10,Fdisclosed by the Cabinet Office in
OL,11,Fresponse to a "humble address" motion
OL,12,F` a rarely used parliamentary
OL,13,Fmanoeuvre that compels the government
OL,14,Fto act.
OL,16,FThe 31 files released on Wednesday did
OL,17,Fnot include correspondence between No
OL,18,F10 and Lord Mandelson, in which a
OL,19,Fnumber of follow-up questions were
OL,20,Fasked about his relationship with
OL,21,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,26,@sD@OOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMPs have been told those exchanges
OL,8,Fremain subject to the Metropolitan
OL,9,FPolice's ongoing investigation into
OL,10,Fthe peer over allegations of
OL,11,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,13,FThe prime minister is facing fresh
OL,14,Fquestions about his judgment in giving
OL,15,FLord Mandelson the ambassadorship
OL,16,Fdespite the files revealing he was
OL,17,Fwarned of a "general reputational
OL,18,Frisk" because of his relationship with
OL,19,FEpstein.
OL,26,@yD@MOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSenior officials also had concerns
OL,8,Fabout his appointment, with National
OL,9,FSecurity Adviser Jonathan Powell
OL,10,Fbelieving the process was "weirdly
OL,11,Frushed", the papers showed.
OL,13,FPressed on why Starmer had not felt it
OL,14,Fnecessary to speak with the peer
OL,15,Fpersonally before the appointment, No
OL,16,F10 repeated the "full process that was
OL,17,Fin place at the time was followed".
OL,26,@rD@[OUsD@GO]xD@QOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe spokesman added: "You heard from
OL,8,Fthe prime minister yesterday when he
OL,9,Freiterated his apology to the victims
OL,10,Fof Jeffrey Epstein for appointing
OL,11,FPeter Mandelson."
OL,13,FOn Thursday, Starmer took
OL,14,Fresponsibility for the "mistake" of
OL,15,Fappointing the peer, but Downing
OL,16,FStreet denied suggestions of a "cover-
OL,17,Fup" and said no notes by the prime
OL,18,Fminister were redacted.
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@QO]vD@XOUvD@`O]xD@`OUyD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"There are a range of different ways
OL,8,Fin which the prime minister's senior
OL,9,Fteam responds to advice," his
OL,10,Fspokesman said.
OL,12,FWriting to Sir Laurie on Thursday,
OL,13,Fshadow Cabinet Office minister Alex
OL,14,FBurghart suggested there was "missing"
OL,15,Fcorrespondence in the published
OL,16,Fmaterial, and that complying only
OL,17,Fpartially with the humble address may
OL,18,Fbe a contempt of parliament.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@YO]vD@^OUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe also questioned why published files
OL,8,Frelating to a fact-finding process
OL,9,Fsurrounding Lord Mandelson's dismissal
OL,10,Fdid not include discussions with key
OL,11,Ffigures like then-No 10 chief of staff
OL,12,FMorgan McSweeney or the prime minister
OL,13,Fhimself.
OL,15,FBut Sir Laurie said it was "not within
OL,16,Fmy remit to investigate the actions or
OL,17,Fdecisions taken by particular
OL,18,Fdepartments, or by the government more
OL,19,Fbroadly".
OL,26,@wD@\OU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSome files which touch on national
OL,8,Fsecurity or foreign relations matters
OL,9,Fwill be redacted but the final say on
OL,10,Fthat rests with parliament's
OL,11,Fintelligence and security committee.
OL,13,FJust one of the documents released on
OL,14,FWednesday was redacted in agreement
OL,15,Fwith the committee.
OL,17,FThe government has also agreed a
OL,18,Fframework with Scotland Yard on which
OL,19,Fdocuments can be released without
OL,20,Fprejudicing the ongoing investigation
OL,21,Finto the former ambassador.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773436320
OL,3,C'No requirement' for PM to interview
OL,4,CMandelson for ambassadorship, No 10
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FLord Mandelson was arrested on
OL,8,FFebruary 23 on suspicion of misconduct
OL,9,Fin public office, having been accused
OL,10,Fof passing sensitive information to
OL,11,FEpstein during his time as business
OL,12,Fsecretary in Gordon Brown's government.
OL,14,FHe was subsequently bailed, but later
OL,15,Freleased from his bail conditions,
OL,16,Falthough he remains under
OL,17,Finvestigation.
OL,19,FHe has said, via his lawyers, that he
OL,20,Flooks forward to clearing his name.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
